{"tid":1709832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非新職業]塞交通工具-廚魔法師","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T04:26:59.000Z","uid":123456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5697b3f537035f904a0b419668a5e1c38b21d3","tid":1709832,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"三罷唔要塞交通工具<br />\n唔一定要人塞<br />\n聽過人咁做，咪撚咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔可以用放置調味料塞<br />\n搞到人唔敢企埋去<br />\n變相0人塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要攞米豬連5星星<br />\n一定要色，香味俱全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首選紅醋：見紅成篤m咁已經唔想踩，個味仲要咁撚大(利申鼓油撚) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次選醋，但唔好撞色倒喺非黑位置優先，都係咁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n製彈：各大奶共餐廳調味料櫃自取，一包包嗰啲，唔好唔幫襯就咁攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放彈：陰暗處自己撕開一角，要好細忽，驚佢漏出黎搞到自己，再偷偷放置喺地(可以用放低袋做cover)﹐最後臨轉位/走唔好輕踩，m血已漏，出撚曬水，臭過臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519e66e9eb859e15c6d701cd31dded0ce8ef25b8","tid":1709832,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1aadd0b984bd1966cb30d1c6bb6314acecc5f082","tid":1709832,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9d68bb586aba9c608d6615ddc9dc3fd542ab77fe","tid":1709832,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a04e7a8dfdd4333a423ae2dd7c313545b27e156","tid":1709832,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0a0fe46bb0d92e8a8d7cb756178afce6f0fa7c1f","tid":170